AUTHOR: - LaMar -

DESCRIPTION:
this program is use to adjust the alsa_mixer volume.
=========================================================
USAGE:
up:./volume -c <cardId> -m <mixerName> up ;  exp: ./volume -c 0 -m Master up

down:./volume -c <cardId> -m <mixerName> down; exp: ./volume -c 0 -m Master down

BUILD:
just make in the current directory.
